{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_08_01_short",
  "title": "川咲さくら 1話 頑張ります、コーチ！ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日の練習、凄く良かったよ\nこれなら大阪公演も成功間違いなしだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The practice today was great.\nWith this‚ the Osaka performance will surely be a success.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにそう言ってもらえるなら\n安心です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you say so‚ {user}-san‚\nI’m relieved!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7625168641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.3958501975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピース初の全国ツアーも、そろそろ折り返しだ\nだいぶ疲れが溜まってるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re almost halfway through Sunny Peace’s first national tour.\nYou must be pretty tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "明日と明後日は久しぶりのオフだ。英気を養ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have a long-awaited break tomorrow and the day after. Recharge yourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4892730712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.1808142502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あのー、そのオフなんですけど\n付き合ってほしい所があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ about the break…\nI have a place I’d like to go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8474809169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　別にいいけど、どうして俺なんだ？\nせっかくのオフだし、メンバー同士で行けば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? That’s fine‚ but why me?\nIt’s a precious day off‚ why don’t you go with the other members…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0601334571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、{user}さんに\nお願いしたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ {user}-san‚\nI want to go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3601334571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのためにも、力を貸してもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the fans‚ could you lend me a hand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0268016497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "近い、近いって。分かったから内容を話してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re too close‚ too close! I get it‚ so just tell me what it’s about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6934667905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.6379562537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私、応援したい人がいるんです\nそのために、力を貸してほしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to cheer for someone up.\nThat’s why I want your help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0046229203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "応援……？　もしかして、全国ツアーを回りながら\nファンの願いを叶える、あの企画か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cheer…? Is this about that project where you go around\nthe country on tour and fulfill fans’ wishes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}